{"ID":"20240910135348-jhgidrv","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240910135348-jhgidrv","title":"Git 不同仓库用不同的用户名和邮箱","type":"doc","updated":"20240910135502"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240910135400-576wakr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-576wakr","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在 Git 中，你可以根据不同的远端仓库（如 GitHub 和 Gitee）使用不同的用户名和邮箱。实现这个功能的步骤如下："}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-mf7u1ri","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-mf7u1ri","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1. 配置全局用户名和邮箱"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-m6jukmn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-m6jukmn","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先，配置全局的用户名和邮箱，这会作为默认设置使用。你可以通过以下命令设置："}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-1c74ch2","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-1c74ch2","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"git config --global user.name \"Your Global Username\"\ngit config --global user.email \"your_global_email@example.com\"\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-biagnwu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-biagnwu","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2. 针对特定仓库配置用户名和邮箱"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-xzwh0rd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-xzwh0rd","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可以为每个 Git 仓库单独设置用户名和邮箱。在特定项目的目录下执行以下命令："}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-7au1w6c","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-7au1w6c","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"git config user.name \"Your Project-Specific Username\"\ngit config user.email \"your_project_specific_email@example.com\"\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-k548y30","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-k548y30","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这会将 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"user.name"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 和 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"user.email"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 设置为当前仓库的配置，而不会影响其他仓库。"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-b7a2xqe","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-b7a2xqe","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3. 针对不同远端仓库使用不同用户名和邮箱"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-x2hu1v7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-x2hu1v7","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你在一个项目中同时使用 GitHub 和 Gitee，你可以通过 Git 钩子或使用 Git 的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"includeIf"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 功能来自动切换用户名和邮箱。"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-upmw92o","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-upmw92o","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法一：使用 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".git/config"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 文件设置远端配置"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-qnde7p4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-qnde7p4","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你可以直接修改项目根目录下的 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":".git/config"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 文件，针对不同的远端设置特定的用户名和邮箱。例如："}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-729ltgn","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-729ltgn","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"YmFzaA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"[remote \"origin\"]\n    url = git@github.com:your_github_account/your_repo.git\n    fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/origin/*\n\n[remote \"gitee\"]\n    url = git@gitee.com:your_gitee_account/your_repo.git\n    fetch = +refs/heads/*:refs/remotes/gitee/*\n\n# GitHub 用户名和邮箱\n[branch \"master\"]\n    remote = origin\n    merge = refs/heads/master\n    user.name = \"Your GitHub Username\"\n    user.email = \"your_github_email@example.com\"\n\n# Gitee 用户名和邮箱\n[branch \"dev\"]\n    remote = gitee\n    merge = refs/heads/dev\n    user.name = \"Your Gitee Username\"\n    user.email = \"your_gitee_email@example.com\"\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20240910135400-0hhnkck","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240910135400-0hhnkck","updated":"20240910135400"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这样，根据你在哪个分支或远端工作，Git 会自动使用对应的用户名和邮箱。"}]}]}